Salesforce.com Inc Signs Definitive Agreement to Acquire Buddy Media
Monday, 4 Jun 2012 06:00am EDT
Salesforce.com Inc announced that it has entered into a definitive agreement to acquire Buddy Media, social media marketing platform, for approximately $689 million payable in cash and salesforce.com equity. The transaction is expected to be completed during salesforce.com's fiscal third quarter ending October 31, 2012. Salesforce.com will acquire Buddy Media for approximately $467 million in cash and $184 million in salesforce.com common stock, and $38 million in vested salesforce.com options and restricted stock units. CODE Advisors acted as the exclusive financial advisor to Buddy Media.Â 
